gather (0.4.1)

  * possibility to collect data not only with minute but also
    with second or hour granularity added;

  * more correct handling of timeperiod '$' -- date of the last
    collection;

  * cleanup and bugfixes;

  * improved documentation and examples.

-- Mikolaj Golub <to.my.trociny@gmail.com> 2012/05/26

gather (0.4.0)

  * die when failing to eval configs;

  * script command added;

  * archive command added;

  * plot command added (gnuplot is required).

-- Mikolaj Golub <to.my.trociny@gmail.com> 2010/10/24

gather (0.3.0)

  * autoconfiguration (run make to generate utility and man);

  * possibility to run commands in parallel;

  * show assemble -- assemble entries by regexp with key/value pair.

-- Mikolaj Golub <to.my.trociny@gmail.com> 2010/02/14

gather (0.2)

  * some bug fixes and timeperiod shortcuts.

-- Mikolaj Golub <to.my.trociny@gmail.com> 2008/12

gather (0.1)

  * initial version.

-- Mikolaj Golub <to.my.trociny@gmail.com> 2008/09
